    dc:creator "Avila, Luciano Javier; Morando, Mariana; Perez, Cristian Hernan Fulvio; Sites, Jack W." ;
    dc:date "2007" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Liolaemus (Reptilia: Squamata: Liolaemini) from southern Mendoza province, Argentina" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176277>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176278>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176279>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176280> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176277>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Liolaemus puelche, holotype adult male (MACN 38992), from south side of Ruta Nacional 40, 3 km N Ranquil Norte, Malargüe Department, Mendoza province, Argentina." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176277/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176278>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dorsal and ventral color variation in the type series of Liolaemus puelche." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176278/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176279>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Type locality of Liolaemus puelche (black dot). Grey lines show main national and provincial roads, and open circles identify main towns in the region. Insert: the area in Argentina." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176279/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176280>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. General view of the type locality of Liolaemus puelche from a northern perspective. Lizard activity was more intense under the large shrubs of Schinus johnstonii." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176280/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

